ARM: imx_v4_v5_defconfig: Update defconfig

Select the following drivers to be built by default:
- SMSC911x
- LCD_L4F00242T0 (LCD present on mx27pdk)
- CONFIG_VIDEO_MX2
- OV2640 (Camera present on mx27pdk)
